    "description": "<p>\r\n\tChina State Construction Engineering Corporation Limited Singapore Branch (CSCEC) is China's largest construction and real estate conglomerate and biggest building work contractor.  It operates in more than 20 countries and regions around the world.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tThe Singapore branch's main business focus is on Civil Engineering and currently we have 2 MRT projects on the Down Town Line 3.  It is our long-term objective to expand our operation in Singapore and to build a strong human capital base here to tap into the growth of the infrastructure and construction industry in this region.</p>\r\n",
